articles.title: Big Tech companies, foreign governments scramble after Trump slaps $100,000 annual fee on H-1B visas - CNBC
articles.description: The announcement to impose a $100,000 annual fee on H-1B visas sent shockwaves through corporate America.
articles.content: Major technology companies and foreign governments are rushing to respond after President Donald Trump late Friday announced plans to impose a $100,000 annual fee on H-1B visas, threatening to upend … [+2670 chars]
